      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@\n+---\n+title: Default to 2-digit entry identifiers\n+type: change\n+authors:\n+- codex\n+created: 2025-10-24\n+---\n+\n+Shorten newly generated changelog entry IDs to two digits, restart the unreleased queue at `01`, and continue supporting longer prefixes automatically once we eventually exceed 99 entries."
